Question 2

/* Question 2 */
Libname orasas "C:\Users\Harry Lu's X1\Documents\Cornell\STSCI 5060\HW 4";
Title1 "Question 2";
Title2 "Output 1";

PROC SQL;
    Connect To Oracle As myconn (User = "Da" Password = "950511");
        Execute (Create Table PTF_t As
                        Select Customer_T.CustomerID, Customer_T.CustomerName,
                                Customer_T.CustomerState, Customer_T.CustomerPostalCode
                        From Customer_T INNER JOIN Order_T
                        On Customer_T.CustomerID = Order_T.CustomerID)
        By myconn;
        Disconnect From myconn;
QUIT;
PROC ACCESS Dbms = Oracle;
    Create orasas.PTF_t.access;
        User = "Da";
        Password = "950511";
        Table = PTF_t;
        Assign = yes;
        Rename CustomerID = C_ID;
        Rename CustomerName = C_N;
        Rename CustomerState = C_S;
        Rename CustomerPostalCode = C_PC;
        List All;
    Create orasas.PTF_t.view;
        Select CustomerID CustomerName CustomerState CustomerPostalCode;
RUN;
PROC PRINT Data = orasas.PTF_t Label;
    Label C_ID = "Customer ID" C_N = "Customer Name" C_S = "Customer State" C_PC = "Customer Postal Code";
RUN;
